title: GTA Executive Director Elected NASCIO Secretary-Treasurer (GTA - Georgia Technology Authority)
text: ( Source : GTA - Georgia Technology Authority ) The National Association of State Chief Information Officers (NASCIO) elected Calvin Rhodes , Georgia State CIO and GTA Executive Director , as Secretary and Treasurer for the 2015-2016 program
